<class module="driver" runtimeProfile="rt" qualifiedName="javax.baja.driver.util.BDescriptorDeviceExt" name="BDescriptorDeviceExt" packageName="javax.baja.driver.util" public="true">
<description>
DeviceExt that manages failure retries and status for a set of &#xa; descriptors.&#xa; &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Retry&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xa; The retry action is invoked by the retry trigger for the interval configured&#xa; by a user.  The rety action simply calls excute on any descriptors whose&#xa; status is fault.
</description>
